"""Server branding assets (issue #14 / connector identity).

The MCP client shows this logo + name wherever it surfaces the connector. We serve the icon
from the MCP domain (``/favicon.svg``, ``/favicon.ico``, ``/icon.png``) AND advertise it in the
MCP ``serverInfo`` (``website_url`` + ``icons``), so a spec-aware client renders our brand
instead of its generic placeholder. The mark is the same green grid as the website favicon.
The PNG is embedded as base64 to avoid any packaging/static-file pitfalls in the container."""
